{"about_the_game":"<strong>Gameplay :</strong><br><br>The game is a hybrid maze crawler / first person shooter with time manipulation, set inside a claustrophobic air duct filled with deadly traps and unpredictable enemies, you must carefully mark your path and avoid the many obstacles laid out for you all while evading or killing whatever is hunting you inside the maze.<br>Whenever you're in need for resources you can play a round of russian roulette, the riskier you bet the higher your rewards will be.<br>it's recommended that you map the layout of the maze as you progress. <br><br><br><strong>Plot:</strong><br><br>The last thing you remember is buying a vhs tape from an underground movie store run by a mysterious figure, this very same tape transported you to an unusual airduct-like maze where you soon realize that you're not the only one crawling within, and everything is set out to kill you, the question is, what's the real reason you're here?.......<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>VHS inspired aesthetic set inside a claustrophobic environment.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Limited number of retries and permadeath should you die repeatedly.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique gunplay with manual bullet by bullet reloading.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Time manipulation abilities and varying enemies to encounter.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You'll have to escape within a set time limit, and the timer is also your health points.</li></ul><br>Don't forget to mark your path as your traverse the maze.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2682210/extras/MARK.gif?t=1724188785\" /><br><br><br>Unique twist on the infamous Russian roulette where you have to play in order to gain the limited resources which will help you survive, the riskier you play the bigger your rewards will be.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as